  <p class="">I didn’t want you to read this post. Not because it’s bad or anything; because nothing that I tell you about Prague will ever live up to experiencing it first-hand.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Still, you need to know what you’re going to do when you’re in Prague.&nbsp;</p><p class="">So to help you plan your Prague itinerary, here are five, must-see sites to visit in The Mother of Cities at an incredibly good rate.&nbsp;</p><h1><strong>TABLE OF CONTENTS:&nbsp;</strong></h1><ol data-rte-list="default"><li><h2><a href="#point-one-prague-castle" target="_blank">Explore Prague Castle</a></h2></li><li><h2><a href="#point-two-charles-bridge" target="_blank">Stroll Across Charles Bridge</a></h2></li><li><h2><a href="#point-three-old-town-square" target="_blank">Experience the Old Town Square</a></h2></li></ol>





















  
  






  <h3>1. Explore Prague Castle</h3>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
