  <p class="">Notable pubs that you could visit include: <a href="https://www.mccarthys.cz/"><span>McCarthy's Irish Pub</span></a>, <a href="https://aulddubliner.cz/"><span>The Dubliner Irish Bar</span></a>, and <a href="https://mypeople.cz/"><span>My People’s Bar</span></a> among <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=prague+pubs&amp;sca_esv=5576be18993fc50e&amp;sca_upv=1&amp;rlz=1C5CHFA_enCA861CA861&amp;biw=1280&amp;bih=641&amp;sxsrf=ADLYWIK8_qx72bDGiMiGKZn3xAsAyXITxg%3A1727045788609&amp;ei=nKDwZsP8JLjfp84PxP7fSA&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjDuvb10teIAxW478kDHUT_FwkQ4dUDCA8&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=prague+pubs&amp;gs_&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp&amp;lqi=CgtwcmFndWUgcHVic0i1yvXv5YCAgAhaFRABGAEiC3ByYWd1ZSBwdWJzKgIIA5IBCWlyaXNoX3B1YpoBJENoZERTVWhOTUc5blMwVkpRMEZuU1VNdGIxbzJYelJCUlJBQqoBPRABKggiBHB1YnMoADIeEAEiGv6gvpabXxugZItDoLAbB8KZYk1HxN4G8UaxMg8QAiILcHJhZ3VlIHB1YnM#rlimm=13236888925113861342"><span>many</span></a>. And as I mentioned, most of them have great food.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Anyways, get your bags ready, and go out and experience Prague. Hopefully some of these tips are enough to get you started.&nbsp;</p><p class="">If you like our content and want to receive more tips on what to do in each place you visit, consider subscribing to our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Resilience-Routes/61551906447595/"><span>Facebook</span></a>, <a href="https://x.com/R_Routes"><span>Twitter / X</span></a>, and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/resilienceroutes/?next=%2F"><span>Instagram</span></a> channels to receive immediate content that’ll help <em>you </em>navigate your travels the moment it’s released.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Have fun! Enjoy the cheap beer and halusky.&nbsp;</p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>How You Can Prevent Backpacking Burnout &amp; Stay Motivated On Your Adventures</title><dc:creator>Michael Boroda</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 02:14:39 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.resilienceroutes.com/blog/how-you-can-prevent-backpacking-burnout-amp-stay-motivated-on-your-adventures</link><guid isPermaLink="false">64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588:64fce74e086c7e17fabddba4:66de04aedf3d191e7f4ac4de</guid><description><![CDATA[I remember, on my travels, how much fun it was to explore the world, visit 
