          </figcaption>
        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Many travel credit cards offer special rewards and bonuses when you dine out - like the <a href="https://www.americanexpress.com/en-ca/credit-cards/cobalt-card/?cpid=100546623&amp;dsparms=dc_pcrid_700216673716_kword_credit%20card%20for%20entertainment_match_b&amp;ds_rl=1267527&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwj9-zBhDyARIsAERjds0OugsGTiUkjdJhDfZ2uwPOA9JMeK4ss2PCQ_x-qzddsb6__v-3RX0aAklQEALw_wcB&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds"><span>American Express Cobalt® Card</span></a>, the <a href="https://www.cibc.com/en/personal-banking/credit-cards/all-credit-cards/aventura-visa-infinite-privilege-card.html?utrc=S229:252&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwj9-zBhDyARIsAERjds16RtTDI2BFkKUTCMoV3R2hUopMhvswnnE1jgZz8Bxs4LallNRIoEIaAi6TEALw_wcB&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds"><span>CIBC Aventura® Visa Infinite Privilege* Card</span></a>, or the <a href="https://www.td.com/ca/en/personal-banking/products/credit-cards/aeroplan/aeroplan-visa-infinite-privilege-card"><span>TD® Aeroplan® Visa Infinite Privilege* credit card</span></a> in Canada, and the <a href="https://applynow.capitalone.com/?irgwc=1&amp;external_id=IRAFF_ZZ7561ce79cd714920a6adb8b9424e4d1a_USCIR_K170911_A344893L_C19d37b9fN31bb11efa5664d695578d74_S_P&amp;pscid=&amp;transid=&amp;marketingChannel=P23235&amp;oC=COh7rTP9h&amp;applicationprefillid=&amp;productId=28651"><span>Capital One SavorOne Cash Rewards credit card</span></a>, the <a href="https://creditcards.chase.com/a1/24Q3/sapphire/goreserve?CELL=6H8X&amp;AFFID=SWlnSnn6x54-VpVSU6fsdLanqvyTy.glig&amp;pvid=66418be57fc248cdb7c92585ab65b193&amp;jp_cmp=cc/1598517/aff/15-31810/na"><span>Chase Sapphire Reserve card</span></a>, and the <a href="https://secure.bankofamerica.com/apply-credit-cards/public/icai-single/#/info/"><span>Bank of America Customized Cash Rewards credit card</span></a> in the U.S., to name a few.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Bet you didn’t know that, huh?</p><p class="">If you want to take advantage of these strategies on your travels, then look for cards that provide extra points for dining purchases, or have partnerships with specific restaurants or food delivery services.&nbsp;</p><p class="">For example, <a href="https://creditcards.chase.com/rewards-credit-cards/sapphire/preferred"><span>Chase Sapphire Preferred</span></a> offers 3x points on dining worldwide - including delivery and takeout services.&nbsp;</p><p class="">You can then use these points to redeem for dining gift cards, statement credits, or even direct bookings at exclusive restaurants through your card’s travel portal.</p><p class="">While this may require a bit of forethought if you plan to travel to specific destinations, it’s worth it for the amount of benefits you can rack up through dining points.&nbsp;</p><p class="">After all, if you’re going to eat, why not earn while you’re doing it?&nbsp;</p>





















  
  






  <p class="">       2. Utilize Airline and Hotel Loyalty Programs for Dining Deals</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1920x2880" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w" width="1920" height="2880" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/89bbd1a0-d784-4003-94df-271e217c5f03/alev-takil-lw3Lqe2K7xc-unsplash.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
          
