  <p class="">This is just the tip of the iceberg of the things you can see, do, and experience in Lucerne, all by walking / hiking, and all of which cost little to no money.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Now that we’ve got that out of the way, let’s discuss…</p>





















  
  






  <p class="">2. Across the Waters: Ferry Adventures on Lake Lucerne</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG" data-image-dimensions="4032x3024" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=1000w" width="4032" height="3024" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/769bbf02-6c24-4d37-a486-2f629c341e85/IMG_2840.JPG?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">One of the best things you could do in Lucerne is take the <a href="https://www.lakelucerne.ch/en/your-cruise-experience/timetable-fares/"><span>ferry / sightseeing cruise</span></a> across Lake Lucerne.&nbsp;</p><p class="">While not especially different from sightseeing cruises you may have taken in other cities, Lucerne stands out in its scenery, with its stunning Swiss Alps, and lakeside cottages surrounding your voyage. The tour also comes with an <a href="https://www.getyourguide.com/lucerne-l867/lucerne-1-hour-cruise-on-panoramic-yacht-t41946?partner_id=JCSGAIF&amp;psrc=partner_api&amp;currency=CHF&amp;mkt_cmp=true&amp;lang=en&amp;date_from=2024-05-21&amp;_pc=1,1"><span>audio guide</span></a>!&nbsp;</p><p class="">So make sure to get a ticket and book a one hour sightseeing tour, which admittedly is a little bit pricey, and usually costs about 32 CHF - $48 CAD or $35 USD - and it’s worth it - if you plan your budget accordingly that is.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Still hesitant? Check out some of the photos that I took below, and see for yourself if it’s worth it for you:&nbsp;</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
