            <p class="">You get the point. </p>
          </figcaption>
        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">3. Lucerne's Double Delight: Ice Cream and Chocolate Factory Finds</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG" data-image-dimensions="3024x4032" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=1000w" width="3024" height="4032" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/64fce6ab35ce4611b9594588/b89241a8-e839-4ba6-9143-5f2ab8c7c98a/IMG_2270.JPG?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
          
          <figcaption class="image-caption-wrapper">
            <p class="">Ice cream cone from Bachman’s. </p>
          </figcaption>
        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">And finally, we have what Switzerland is known for: chocolate.&nbsp;</p><p class="">There are several chocolate shops and factories you could visit while you’re here, including <a href="https://www.lindt.ch/de/"><span>Lindt</span></a>, <a href="https://laderach.com/ch-de/"><span>Läderach</span></a>, and <a href="https://www.maxchocolatier.com/"><span>Max Chocolatier Boutique</span></a>.&nbsp;</p><p class="">There are also lots of really good ice cream stands and shops. While not exactly the gelato king like Italy, Switzerland has really good ice cream, and Lucerne has plenty of gelaterias; cafes where you can get a really good cone for a pricey yet worth it cost.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Some of the best ice cream shops in Lucerne include <a href="https://www.amorino.com/de/"><span>Amorino</span></a> - an Italian gelato chain -, <a href="https://www.alpineum.lu/gelateriadellalpi/"><span>Gelateria dell'Alpi</span></a>, and my personal favorite, <a href="https://www.confiserie.ch/de/"><span>Bachman</span></a>, a bakery whose <a href="https://www.confiserie.ch/gelateria-am-quai"><span>Gelateria on the quay location in Lucerne</span></a> has the most delicious cones and ice cream that I had while I was there. Again, it’s a little more on the expensive side, and that’s Switzerland.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
